Package de.gnwi.spicestographstream

Spices to GraphStream Wrapper:
The SpicesToGraphStreamModel class and its supporting classes in this package are designed to create a GraphStream graph from a SPICES line notation / Spices object.

See: Description

    SpicesToGraphStream

    Constants.Shape
    An enum for the GraphStream node shape options (see StyleConstants.Shape) which gives the keyword that must be added as a 'ui.style' attribute to a node.

Package de.gnwi.spicestographstream Description

Spices to GraphStream Wrapper:
The SpicesToGraphStreamModel class and its supporting classes in this package are designed to create a GraphStream graph from a SPICES line notation / Spices object.
